race.comment: LOWESTOFT (9) looks well placed to break through. She's placed in all three runs this time in, sticking on well at Cranbourne behind a handy winner last time out having just found one better at Sale prior. Comes back a notch here and sets up for every hope. SILVASISTA (12) resumes for her second campaign. She placed in a rich race on debut at Swan Hill. Wary with natural improvement. SO VOGUE (5) resumes. He got over more ground last time in but this is a good trip to kick off at and he can be running on well. MAYEKI (10) struggled fresh at Geelong but will strip much fitter and can improve quickly.
